These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, basketball, skiing
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | skiing | basketball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, reading, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | singing | drawing | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, water
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking water##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | cola | sprite | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, water
1. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea | mirinda |

